CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773349950
OL,3,CTwo charged in connection with crash
OL,4,Cthat killed 'caring' husband
OL,6,FBoth men have been remanded into
OL,7,Fcustody and are due to appear at
OL,8,FStockport Magistrates' Court.
OL,10,FPaying tribute to Mr Abayomi after his
OL,11,Fdeath, his partner Denise said: "He
OL,12,Fwas the most caring soul and gentle
OL,13,Fperson you could ever meet. He had
OL,14,Ftime for everybody and is loved by
OL,15,Feveryone. Syll will be sadly missed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
